      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "When the foundation of your identity feels gone, the idea of \"wholeness\" can seem impossible. It might be helpful to shift focus from finding your old soul to experimenting with small, neutral feelings or sensations rather than intense emotion. Even tiny acts of caring for yourself, like a specific routine or a comforting sound, can be an act of tending to the house, even if it feels empty. Please remember that you deserve support during this deep void.",
      "source": "target",
